#finetune outputs, all reproducible: the scripts remake the jsonls and csv,
#the model itself lives on hugging face. every training jsonl lives in
#traindata/ so a new one needs no new line here. train_rewordings.jsonl is the
#exception, hand written and not regenerable, so it stays tracked.
#the star matters: "traindata/" alone stops git descending and the ! never fires
finetune/mtg-tuned-*/
finetune/traindata/*
!finetune/traindata/train_rewordings.jsonl
finetune/bakeoff_results.csv
finetune/sanity_report.txt
